JOHANNESBURG, South Africa, July 13, 2020/APO Group/ -- 
                                                        
                            A total of 45821 COVID-19 tests were conducted in the last 24 hours. Regrettably, we report 108 more COVID-19 related deaths, bringing the total number of deaths to 4079. The number of recoveries is 138874 (48.8% recovery rate). Thank you to all the healthcare workers.